headline: Will Block's (SQ) Grubhub Integration Test the Restaurant Tech Innovation Narrative?
summary: Block, Inc. recently announced an expanded partnership with Grubhub, integrating Square's point-of-sale system with the food delivery platform and introducing Cash App Pay for Grubhub customers, all as part of a suite of major food and beverage platform innovations.
